	<h1 class="title">为了让你接受 AR，微软在第五大道开了个 HoloLens 体验馆</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/43366/small/43366.jpg?1430896699" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王民超 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-21 06:31:14 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19398/medium/19398.jpg?1450448403" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


